###Chatbot & LLM Evaluation

## Overview
This repository presents an evaluation of conversational AI systems, including **ELIZA** and modern **instruction-tuned LLMs**. Systems were tested for **coherence**, **instruction-following**, and **relevance** in response to user prompts.  

The lab demonstrates the differences between **rule-based chatbots** and modern **LLMs**, highlighting the strengths of instruction-tuned models for chatbot tasks.

## Tools
- Python
- Hugging Face Transformers

